text: Very very very nice ba chor mee. Ask for extra vinegar and extra chill and the whole bowl of noodle taste so delicious!! Added the meat ball soup and it is so good! Will definitely visit again.

meatball noodles were reasonable but meatballs tasted weird for me.
Average fish dumplings soup , goes well with chilli from prawn noodle stall

It deserves to be called out that the minced pork in the bakchormee is pre-cooked.
You decide for yourself if you wanna have that.
The sauce mix makes up for that though.

One of the better fishball and minced pork noodles in Bukit Panjang. The fishball is bouncy and nice. The chilli sauce goes very nicely with the noodles, especially when vinegar is added. You can add as much condiments especially the fried shallots and spring onion as you like. Great for a quick and fuss free meal.
I liked the Bak Chor Mee
